---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const post = {
  title: "Explore the Next Generation of Interactivist Interventions",
  subtitle: "Building the 5th generation disinformation intervention cookbook",
  date: "June 20, 2023",
  authors: "DROG Team",
  category: "Research",
  readTime: "6 min read"
};
---

<Layout title={post.title} description="Your disinformation interventions must constantly deal with, and adapt to new circumstances, whilst taking on board scientific insights and field lab testing.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="post-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/blog" class="back-link">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        Back to Blog
      </a>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-category">{post.category}</span>
        <span class="post-date">{post.date}</span>
        <span class="post-read-time">{post.readTime}</span>
      </div>
      <h1>{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="post-subtitle">{post.subtitle}</p>
      <div class="post-authors">
        <span>By {post.authors}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <article class="post-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <p class="lead">Your disinformation interventions must constantly deal with, and adapt to new circumstances, whilst taking on board scientific insights and field lab testing. We are currently exploring how to properly productise new additions to the disinformation intervention cookbook.</p>

        <p>Read more about these so-called "Interactivist" 5th-generation interventions.</p>

        <div class="callout-box">
          <div class="callout-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="callout-content">
            <h3>The Core Insight</h3>
            <p>People change their minds mainly through interacting with other people. Under the right conditions, others can help us find errors in our beliefs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>What are Interactivist Interventions?</h2>
        <p>Interactivist interventions represent the fifth generation of counter-disinformation approaches in the DROG DIM model. Unlike previous generations that focused on individual cognition or information access, Interactivist interventions recognize that people change their minds mainly through interacting with other people.</p>

        <h2>The Problem We're Addressing</h2>
        <p>Generation 5 interventions respond to societal alienation â€” the growing disconnect between people and communities that makes them vulnerable to disinformation. When people feel isolated, they become more susceptible to narratives that offer simple explanations and in-group belonging.</p>

        <div class="problem-visual">
          <div class="problem-card">
            <span class="problem-label">The Challenge</span>
            <h4>Societal Alienation</h4>
            <p>Growing disconnect between people and communities creates vulnerability to manipulation</p>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-arrow">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-card solution">
            <span class="problem-label">The Solution</span>
            <h4>Social Interactions</h4>
            <p>Meaningful conversations and collaborative error-correction build resilience</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Key Principles</h2>
        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="principle-card">
            <div class="principle-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
                <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Social Interaction First</h4>
            <p>Prioritizing group communication over individual education</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle-card">
            <div class="principle-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/>
                <polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Adaptive Design</h4>
            <p>Constantly evolving based on new circumstances and research</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle-card">
            <div class="principle-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M6 18h8M3 22h18M14 22a7 7 0 1 0 0-14h-1M9 14h2M9 8h2M10 18V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h0a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Scientific Foundation</h4>
            <p>Built on rigorous academic insights and field testing</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle-card">
            <div class="principle-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Practical Application</h4>
            <p>Focused on productizing interventions for real-world deployment</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <p>We are developing interventions that:</p>

        <ul class="approach-list">
          <li>
            <span class="list-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Facilitate meaningful conversations between people with different viewpoints
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Create spaces for collaborative fact-finding and error correction
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Build community resilience against manipulation
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Leverage social dynamics for positive change
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Join the Development</h2>
        <p>We're actively exploring and testing new Interactivist interventions. If you're interested in contributing as a practitioner, scientist, or creative tech, we'd love to hear from you.</p>

        <div class="cookbook-callout">
          <div class="cookbook-emoji">ðŸ“–</div>
          <p><strong>The cookbook is being written â€” and you can help shape the recipes.</strong></p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="post-cta">
          <h3>Ready to contribute?</h3>
          <p>Join our community of practitioners, scientists, and creative techs working on the next generation of interventions.</p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/community" class="btn btn-primary">Join Community</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Related Posts -->
        <div class="related-posts">
          <h3>Related Articles</h3>
          <div class="related-grid">
            <a href="/blog/manifesto-2022-drog-dim" class="related-card">
              <span class="related-category">DIM</span>
              <h4>Manifesto 2022: A Method to Solve the Definitional Problem</h4>
              <span class="related-date">January 2022</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/blog/harmony-square" class="related-card">
              <span class="related-category">Case Studies</span>
              <h4>Harmony Square: A Game About Fake News</h4>
              <span class="related-date">December 2024</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .post-hero {
    padding: 10rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #059669, #10b981, #34d399, #059669);
    background-size: 400% 400%;
    animation: gradient-shift 15s ease infinite;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  @keyframes gradient-shift {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
  }

  .post-hero .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .post-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .post-category {
    background: var(--white);
    color: #059669;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .post-date,
  .post-read-time {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .post-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .post-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .post-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .post-authors {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Content */
  .post-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-wrapper p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Callout Box */
  .callout-box {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #10b981 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .callout-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .callout-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .callout-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem !important;
  }

